Package com.walletapp.model

Class Record

java.lang.Object
com.walletapp.model.Record
public class Record extends Object
Represents a financial record for a user. A record can be of type "Income", "Expense", or a transfer, and may have associated labels. This class also holds joined data from related tables for display purposes.
